  "description": "<p>最近来自美国北卡罗莱纳州中央公园学校Aaron Sebens和所在的四年级同学今年三月份在著名融资平台Kickstarter上尝试进行融资，希望能够获得相关的捐献用来来改善教室的能源输入，在教 室屋顶安装太阳能设备。当时他们的目标是$800，不过两个月之后他们收到了$5817.随后Sebens罗列了一些选购的清单，而今天传来消息称在今年 6月份该教室已经成功使用太阳能能源进行各种操作了。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e46ca4a/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243718.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E7%BA%A7%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%9E%8D%E8%B5%84%E4%B8%BA%E6%95%99%E5%AE%A4%E6%B7%BB%E7%BD%AE%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243718.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E7%BA%A7%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%9E%8D%E8%B5%84%E4%B8%BA%E6%95%99%E5%AE%A4%E6%B7%BB%E7%BD%AE%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243718.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E7%BA%A7%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%9E%8D%E8%B5%84%E4%B8%BA%E6%95%99%E5%AE%A4%E6%B7%BB%E7%BD%AE%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243718.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E7%BA%A7%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%9E%8D%E8%B5%84%E4%B8%BA%E6%95%99%E5%AE%A4%E6%B7%BB%E7%BD%AE%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87